ernate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23971355/black-friday-2023-tech-deals-under-25-cyber-monday</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-27T16:18:07-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-27T16:18:07-05:00</updated><title>您可以获得的 2023 年网络星期一最佳游戏优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;索尼 DualSense 控制器面向前方，靠在 PlayStation 5 控制台的前面。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/D3RMxMjqlIkgsDHME2oMUcUmfkM=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72893119/vpavic_4261_20201023_0020。 6.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Vjeran Pavic / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;SLvuFB&quot;>;现在是储备游戏和游戏配件的最佳时机 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www. theverge.com/23939216/black-friday-guide-cyber-monday-tech-gadgets-2023&quot;>;网络星期一&lt;/a>;，而今年，我们看到今年发布的一些最大的游戏有相当大的折扣 —需要我提醒您的是，这一年里充斥着许多优秀的游戏。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;div id=&quot;csoMnq&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem -component=&quot;aside:11906226&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;pbjdk6&quot;>;虽然并非今年所有最热门的游戏都获得大幅折扣，但诸如 &lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BPMTJJ6D?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;&lt;em>;最终幻想 XVI&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href =&quot;https://click.linksynergy.com/deeplink?id=nOD%2FrLJHOac&amp;mid=24348&amp;amp;u1=verge&amp;amp;murl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamestop.com%2Fvideo-games%2Fproducts%2Fstar- wars-jedi-survivor---playstation-5%2F357738.html&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;&lt;em>;星球大战绝地：幸存者&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;。当谈到稍旧的游戏时，很多，比如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://click.linksynergy.com/deeplink?id=nOD%2FrLJHOac&amp;amp;mid=24348&amp;amp;u1=verge&amp;amp;murl=https%3A%2F %2Fwww.gamestop.com%2Fvideo-games%2Fproducts%2Fdoom-eternal---playstation-4%2F171397.html&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;&lt;em>;毁灭永恒&