e.com/23965961/black-friday-2023-tech-deals-under-100-cyber-monday&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;f5fVhl&quot;>;如果您错过了黑色星期五优惠，幸运的是，网络星期一优惠就在这里，降低了最新 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com 的价格/Apple-Generation-Cancelling-Transparency-Personalized/dp/B0CHWRXH8B/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;AirPods Pro&lt;/a>;，新款&lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.amazon.com/Apple-Smartwatch-Aluminum-Fitness-Tracker/dp/B0CHX92WB8/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;spoken noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Apple Watch 系列 9&lt;/a >;，以及其他苹果设备的价格创历史新低。您还可以在我们的一些更经济实惠的精选产品上获得折扣，包括 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Apple-MX532AM-A-AirTag/dp/B0933BVK6T/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;poned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;AirTags&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Apple-AirPods-Charging-Latest-Model/dp/B07PXGQC1Q?tag =theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;入门级 AirPods&lt;/a>;，以及来自 &lt;a href=&quot;https:// 等产品的一系列与 MagSafe 兼容的充电器www.amazon.com/gp/product/B09BBKHCHF?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;贝尔金&lt;/a>; 等。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;44wxsc&quot; >;下面，我们汇总了您可以找到的最佳 Apple 优惠...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23971262/black-friday-2023-apple-deals -网络星期一&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23971262/black-friday-2023-apple-deals-cyber-monday" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23971262/black-friday-2023-apple-deals-cyber-monday</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-27T16:05:52-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-27T16:05:52-05:00</updated><title>您可以获得耳机和耳塞的最佳网络星期一优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Technics EAH-AZ80 耳塞的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NpwPDzhMc5N1lti7AQkaVnXFlUM=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72876575/DSCF2268.9.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;XXP47s&quot;>;令人难以抗拒的假日促销已经正式到来，许多来自最大科技品牌的耳机和耳塞均打折至黑色星期五和网络星期一的最低价格。如果您一直在推迟购买苹果、索尼、三星、谷歌和其他品牌的产品，那么您可能不会比 2023 年网络星期一的这些早期优惠更好。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;y4FImf&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;网络星期一最佳优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23976342/cyber-monday-2023-best-early-deals-tech-speakers -gadgets&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;网络星期一低于 50 美元的最佳优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23972578/black-friday-2023-tech-deals-under -50-cyber-monday&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;现在最值得购买的无线耳机&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21309820/best-wireless-earbuds&quot;}] }&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;nZTcKO&quot;>;我预计最大的耳机制造商不会很快推出任何重大新产品，因此您无需担心买家的问题如果您决定参与以下任何交易，您会感到后悔。进入寒冷的月份，值得考虑的是，耳机在早上通勤时可以兼作耳罩。但与此同时，它......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23965357/black-friday-2023-headphone-earbuds-deals-cyber-monday&quot; >;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23965357/black-friday-2023-headphone-earbuds-deals-cyber-monday" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23965357/black-friday-2023-headphone-earbuds-deals-cyber-monday</id><author><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-27T15:48:11-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-27T15:48:11-05:00</updated><title>亚马逊斥资 17 亿美元收购 iRobot 的交易遭到一些反对</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;由重叠线条组成的橙色、黑色和棕褐色背景上亚马逊文字标记的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/HTyoMNDWNqCHjLl7IyWFUHPW5U4=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72907001/acastro_STK103__03.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Vju2jv&quot;>;欧盟监管机构已向亚马逊发出一份反对声明，反对该公司以 17 亿美元收购 Roomba 制造商 iRobot 的提议。在&lt;a href=&quot;https://ec.europa.eu/commission/presscorner/detail/en/ip_23_5990&quot;>;一份新闻稿&lt;/a>;中，欧盟委员会表示，它“已告知亚马逊其初步观点：其拟收购 iRobot 可能会限制机器人吸尘器市场的竞争。”&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;uqiKB9&quot;>;亚马逊于 2022 年 8 月宣布 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 2022/8/5/23293349/amazon-acquires-irobot-roomba-robot-vacuums&quot;>;计划收购 iRobot&lt;/a>;。此后，拟议的收购受到了监管机构的审查，欧盟委员会透露了一项调查&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/7/6/23628636/eu-regulators-amazon-irobot-roomba-收购调查&quot;>;2023 年 7 月&lt;/a>;。英国监管机构审查了该交易&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.gov.uk/government/news/amazon-s-purchase-of-roomba-maker-cleared-by-cma&quot;>;但于 6 月份批准了&lt; /a>;.联邦贸易委员会要求亚马逊和 iRobot &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cnn.com/2022/09/20/tech/roomba-amazon-ftc-investigation/index.html&quot;>;提供有关该交易的信息&lt; /a>; 2022 年 9 月。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;tDYnKW&quot;>;欧洲...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/ 27/23978371/eu-european-commission-amazon-irobot-acquisition-restrict-competition&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/27/23978371/eu-european-commission-amazon-irobot-acquisition-restrict-competition" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/27/23978371/eu-european-commission-amazon-irobot-acquisition-restrict-competition</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-27T15:45:18-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-27T15:45:18-05:00</updated><title>网络星期一最佳优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;网络星期一用手机购物的人的明亮彩色矢量插图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/dsf1GiP4Phn-ykVroKnHQ8R1ieQ=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873 /cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72905335/236878_CYBER_WEEK_DEALS_AFernandez.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Aaron Fernandez 为 The